\id TIT - Abureni
\h Atai̠to̠s
\toc3 Atai̠
\toc2 Atai̠to̠s
\toc1 A̠d̠ire wa̠ Apo̠l age̠ agi̠o̠m Atai̠to̠s bho̠
\mt2 A̠d̠ire Wa̠ Apo̠l Age̠ agi̠o̠m
\mt1 Atai̠to̠s
\mt2 Bho̠
\imt1 Otighom
\ip Apo̠l agba a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ a̠ghud̠um, na̠ ado̠l, na̠ agu̠o̠ o̠ni̠ ta̠ a̠rugh agu̠b̠e̠ni̠ ma̠ a̠ma̠rugh ta̠ Akrai̠st, d̠a̠ obhel wa̠ i̠na, sekina̠ Atai̠to̠s i̠gi̠ d̠a̠ ekpe A̠kriti bho̠. I̠na awe̠le̠man Atai̠to̠s i̠se̠ ma̠ okokod̠i a̠nwunom, sekina̠ o̠ro̠ o̠ni̠ we̠mu̠ irileghom raso̠si̠ ya̠ od̠i ma̠ i̠se̠ bho̠. Atai̠to̠s bha̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ e̠ma wa̠ ubhelegi ma̠a̠ Agrik bho̠. Agu̠o̠ o̠gba bha̠ i̠na o̠ni̠ ola̠ utibereni ma̠ o̠tu̠o̠no̠m Akrai̠st ma̠ igiel bho̠ Apo̠l ake̠ ma̠ asu̠gbagba d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠.
\ip A̠lebh onon bha̠ ola̠ ubhin unigha̠ ma̠ Atai̠to̠s a̠limon irileghom, na̠ a̠kikiom, ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠bhin a̠rileghom raso̠si̠ ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ ekpe A̠kiriti bho̠. U̠b̠aram unigha̠ i̠na, ma̠ obhin orileghom a̠kokod̠ia̠n ogbo i̠damaghan, na̠ i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ na̠ a̠ma̠rugh, na̠ o̠nyagh a̠to d̠o̠yo̠ ogboloma̠ i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ igunugha̠. Apo̠l agba nyen i̠d̠i̠ar ya̠ i̠na na̠ aru̠ru̠an ogir d̠a̠ ed̠ia̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ Atai̠to̠s.
\iot Aru̠mu̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ u̠ge̠ bho̠
\io1 Ibheleguma̠ \ior (1:1-4)\ior*
\io1 O̠so̠n ikei d̠a̠ aso̠si̠ \ior (1:5-16) \ior*
\io1 E̠mu̠ a̠fugh a̠kikiom onigha̠ a̠gbo ya̠ na̠ e̠gi̠ ma̠ aso̠si̠ bho̠ \ior (2:1-15) \ior*
\io1 A̠kikiom ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ o̠tu̠o̠no̠m Akrai̠st \ior (3:1-15) \ior*
\c 1
\s1 Ibheleguma̠ ta̠ Apo̠l
\p 
\v 1 Ami̠ Apo̠l ob̠a̠ra̠motu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, o̠ni̠ogir ta̠ A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st na̠ age̠ ma̠ a̠lebh onon na̠ a̠ruom anwa. Na̠ oruom ami̠ ma̠ o̠kpo̠me̠ni̠ rologi ima̠ra̠ ta̠ ogbo ya̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ aso̠n bho̠, ma̠ od̠ighi agu̠o̠ ola̠ awa ta̠ e̠mar e̠mu̠gho̠nyan a̠ga̠i a̠ma̠rugh ya̠ ta̠ etutumeni ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠.
\v 2 Ta̠ awo̠l i̠se̠ sa̠ awa ta̠ e̠te̠i̠ eb̠em ologi a̠ghud̠um kid̠ud̠ul wa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ o̠gba d̠o̠ ma̠ igunugha̠ bho̠, a̠gua̠n kisa̠ e̠mara̠nwunom a̠mite bho̠.
\v 3 D̠a̠ ebula̠ o̠ku̠a sa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ Witenemeni d̠i̠yar a̠muzoghod̠iom a̠d̠ighi ma̠ ola̠ uloghom o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ d̠o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ obhel wa̠ i̠na ato̠ a̠guri bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠b̠eton ogir bho̠ alo̠gh d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ d̠ami̠ ma̠ o̠gba omutiom, d̠a̠ a̠d̠ien agu̠o̠ i̠na a̠ruom ami̠ bho̠.
\v 4 Ami̠ Apo̠l na̠ age̠ na̠ a̠ruom anwa Atai̠to̠s, a̠ga̠i o̠nyi̠ d̠ami̠ d̠a̠ onin ologi ima̠ra̠ bho̠.
\p E̠no̠gho̠man na̠ ekima̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ O̠we̠de̠ bho̠ na̠ A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st Witenemeni d̠i̠yar e̠ro̠ na̠ anwa.
\s1 Ogir ta̠ Atai̠to̠s d̠a̠ A̠kriti
\p 
\v 5 Ami̠ i̠we̠le̠man anwa d̠a̠ ekpe A̠kriti ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ anwa ta̠ a̠selegi ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ od̠id̠ia̠ ma̠ ogir bho̠ omunieni, na̠ o̠so̠n ikei omutiom ke̠ma ke̠ma ma̠ agu̠o̠ ami̠ i̠to̠ inigha̠ nyam bho̠.
\v 6 Okei aro̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ abar o̠li̠o̠m o̠ro̠ d̠o̠, owolom ta̠ onin ani̠ ku̠ku̠m, anwi̠i̠ny d̠o̠yo̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ iya̠ ima̠ra̠ ma̠ Akrai̠st na̠ iya̠ ta̠ obhin ob̠em ologi, iya̠ i̠karabh ya̠ ob̠ologiom o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠, iya̠ orugh d̠o̠ ma̠ ado̠l i̠te̠i̠, bo̠d̠o̠ o̠b̠agh d̠o̠ ma̠ e̠mu̠.
\v 7 Agu̠o̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠rileghom aso̠si̠ na̠ a̠kponom otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠, i̠na na̠ o̠kpe̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ onwuna̠ e̠kal abar ola̠ o̠li̠o̠m, ya̠a̠ aro̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ob̠a̠ra̠motu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠. I̠na ko o̠bu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ozu, ko o̠nu̠r d̠o̠ agam i̠gam, o̠d̠a ma̠ a̠min d̠o̠, o̠ni̠ a̠ponoma̠ d̠o̠. I̠na ko ogba̠gba̠ra̠gha̠n d̠o̠ ma̠ ogbo e̠li̠la ma̠ awai̠.
\v 8 Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠, i̠na aro̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠bhin onyen ologi na̠ a̠d̠ighom isuloma̠, sa̠ a̠ba̠ra̠ ma̠ a̠ma̠rugh igielake̠, sa̠ na̠ a̠sibhom ozu, o̠ni̠ igielake̠, o̠ni̠ e̠b̠ab̠ala, sa̠ na̠ a̠gir iya̠ i̠kpe̠ d̠a̠ obhel wa̠ a̠sora̠n bho̠.
\v 9 I̠na na̠ a̠sibh a̠ga̠i o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ bho̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ u̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ i̠na bho̠ akparame̠ni̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠rue a̠bhin a̠ga̠i atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ bho̠ akpo̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ rologi ipa̠n ogbo, na̠ oselegi amu̠gho̠nyan ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠damaghan bho̠.
\v 10 Ezin bho̠, a̠d̠izo awa na̠ e̠pagi̠raghan, sa̠ na̠ efugh iya̠ i̠te̠i̠ na̠ egelemeni ma̠ igelemeni, okunukun d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io awa ogbo ya̠ na̠ etia̠ ma̠ ipo bho̠.
\v 11 Ya̠a̠, akpe̠ ma̠ okpegi aru̠nu̠ d̠awa, ezin bho̠ awa na̠ e̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ya̠ osora̠n d̠o̠, sa̠ na̠ e̠pi̠e̠gi̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ eghun a̠rutu, ma̠ ebula̠ ikpoki.
\v 12 Odi owil ola̠ A̠kriti na̠ agu̠o̠ eka̠ agba ma̠a̠, “A̠nwunom A̠kriti na̠ e̠gba ma̠ igunugha̠ kigiel kigiel, ibom id̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh ya̠ na̠ e̠basi̠o̠m a̠nwunom, na̠ i̠gbu̠o̠ro̠gbu̠o̠r i̠d̠o̠gho̠d̠o̠gh.”
\v 13 Asu̠gbagba bho̠ ya̠gia̠ga̠i. O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, game̠ ma̠ a̠nigha̠ awa ma̠ ibom bo̠ka̠ rologi ima̠ra̠ d̠awa e̠ghu̠a.
\v 14 Ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ awa ko o̠nagha d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠karabh id̠ud̠ul na̠ asi̠b̠o̠m Ogbo A̠zu bho̠, na̠ i̠to̠to̠gi̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ eghel ya̠gia̠ga̠i bho̠.
\v 15 Kabar kabar ab̠ab̠ala d̠awa ogbo ya̠ i̠b̠ab̠ala bho̠; ya̠a̠, d̠awa ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠pi̠o̠gho̠m sa̠ od̠umom d̠o̠ bho̠, abar e̠b̠ab̠ala ola̠ od̠i na̠ awa bo̠, ya̠a̠, rologi d̠awa na̠ egbiriri a̠ruzu d̠awa na̠ e̠pi̠an.
\v 16 Awa na̠ e̠re̠ma ma̠a̠ awa eloghom A̠zib̠a̠, ya̠a̠ rod̠ighi i̠di̠ar d̠awa na̠ eghel i̠na. Eghenegia̠n awa, i̠b̠agh ma̠ aru̠mu̠ ya̠ o̠nagha d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠, ya̠ orue d̠o̠ ma̠ ogir bebina̠ abar ola̠ aro̠ ma̠ ob̠eb̠i.
\c 2
\s1 A̠ga̠i atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠
\p 
\v 1 Ya̠a̠ anwa, tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ isora̠n o̠ro̠ a̠ga̠i atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠.
\v 2 Kikiome ma̠ ikei ilobhiri a̠nwunom bho̠ ma̠ awa ekimeni ma̠ a̠ruzu, ed̠igh edim, esibhom a̠ruzu, e̠ghu̠a d̠a̠ ima̠ra̠ ologi, enwuna̠ ma̠ etula̠n, na̠ a̠ma̠ne.
\p 
\v 3 Onin agu̠o̠ bho̠, kikiome ma̠ iguda̠ anwani̠ bho̠ ma̠ orugh ado̠l d̠awa o̠gu̠b̠e̠ni̠ a̠ma̠rugh anwani̠ e̠b̠ab̠ala. Awa o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ogbo isorogiom, bo̠d̠o̠ re̠bana ta̠ a̠min, ya̠a̠, awa e̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ ib̠eb̠i i̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠.
\v 4 Sa̠ awa ta̠ ebhin i̠se̠ e̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ ikubh anwani̠ bho̠ ma̠ otula̠n a̠riwolom na̠ anwi̠i̠ny d̠awa,
\v 5 na̠ osibhom a̠ruzu d̠awa, na̠ orugh ado̠l e̠b̠ab̠ala, na̠ ogir ogir d̠a̠ a̠rutu d̠awa, na̠ ogir ib̠eb̠i, na̠ ozuruna̠ eghoi onigha̠ a̠riwolom d̠awa, b̠o̠ka̠ o̠ni̠ na̠ ofugh a̠fugh i̠basi̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.
\v 6 Onin agu̠o̠ bho̠, kpo̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ rologi anwi̠i̠ny oyel bho̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ awa ta̠ esibhom a̠ruzu d̠awa d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar.
\v 7 A̠ma̠rugh d̠oyom ebhon d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ i̠d̠i̠ar ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ a̠nwunom ta̠ e̠bi̠gh e̠ta. Bhine d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um igielake̠ na̠ edim, ma̠ a̠leriom ma̠ agu̠o̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ d̠oyom a̠lei abar ate̠i̠.
\v 8 Ro̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ d̠oyom ebhon e̠ro̠ ma̠ iya̠ ko orue d̠o̠ o̠bi̠gh o̠pi̠e̠, b̠o̠ka̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠damaghan bho̠ ed̠igh ari̠ghe̠l, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ awa ko o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠karabh ola̠ ofugh ogboloma̠ i̠yar.
\v 9 Re̠bana bho̠ ezuruna̠ ma̠ eghoi enigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ inwuna̠ awa bho̠ d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar iya̠ isora̠n. Awa o̠kpalatu̠an d̠o̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ inwuna̠ awa bho̠,
\v 10 bo̠d̠o̠ oniniom d̠o̠ awa. Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠, awa erugh a̠ghud̠um igielake̠ iya̠ ta̠ obhin awa ob̠em ologi, b̠o̠ka̠ eb̠la̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ Witenemeni d̠i̠yar bho̠ ed̠igh e̠b̠e̠l enigha̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar.
\v 11 Ezin bho̠, A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠leriom e̠ne̠ghe̠ d̠o̠yo̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠bhin itenemeni na̠ a̠ruom eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom bho̠.
\v 12 E̠ne̠ghe̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ na̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ i̠yar ogin a̠ma̠rugh ya̠ ko onigha̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ma̠ itutumeni, na̠ i̠karabh e̠ralma e̠mara̠nwunom, ya̠a̠ i̠yar osibhom a̠ruzu d̠i̠yar, orugh a̠ma̠rugh igielake̠ d̠a̠ amu̠m onon.
\v 13 D̠a̠ a̠d̠ien agu̠o̠ i̠yar na̠ ogon itutumeni eb̠em ologi bho̠ na̠ eruoma̠ isosorogia̠n ta̠ Obom A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ Witenemeni d̠i̠yar A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st
\v 14 wa̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ a̠ghud̠um d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ obhin o̠ta i̠yar o̠si̠ghe̠ d̠a̠ a̠d̠ien kere kere i̠karabh, na̠ o̠b̠ab̠alame̠ni̠ i̠yar oguri a̠nwunom iyo̠yo̠, ya̠ ta̠ ebhir ogir ib̠eb̠i.
\p 
\v 15 Tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n, ma̠ akpo̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ rologi ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠nagha nyam bho̠, ma̠ a̠bhin eb̠la̠ a̠limon d̠oyom ma̠ a̠selegi ma̠ a̠risi ya̠ awa na̠ erima̠. Ko orugh agu̠o̠ ola̠ o̠ni̠ ta̠ a̠kpon anwa aki̠ri̠me̠ni̠.
\c 3
\s1 Igire Ma̠ Ib̠eb̠i
\p 
\v 1 Nemeta̠ne awa, ma̠ awa ezuruna̠ ma̠ eghoi enigha̠ ma̠ ogbo irileghom na̠ ra̠dila̠de i̠to̠, e̠nagha ma̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ d̠awa, ema̠ra̠ ma̠ obhin onyen ologi ogir ib̠eb̠i d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ re̠kal.
\v 2 Awa o̠gba d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ e̠pi̠e̠, o̠b̠u̠man d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠b̠e̠m, ya̠a̠ awa erugh ado̠l ekima̠, na̠ a̠ma̠rugh o̠ki̠ri̠me̠ni̠ ozu egboloma̠ ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠.
\p 
\v 3 Ezin bho̠, d̠a̠ obhel ola̠ na̠ a̠ten, abar ola̠ i̠yar u̠mu̠gho̠nyan na̠ o̠ri̠la d̠o̠. I̠yar u̠b̠agh aru̠mu̠, sa̠ a̠d̠ien kere kere i̠karabh e̠ralma, na̠ e̠ralma ipulupul ozu na̠ ipesi, na̠ i̠karabh i̠walama, i̠le̠ge̠ i̠yar ka̠ id̠ighom re̠bana, ma̠ ola̠ i̠yar urugh ado̠l igurumia̠n ologi na̠ a̠gbokia̠n, na̠ o̠lo̠gi̠an a̠d̠ien, sa̠ odi a̠ghir ologi ma̠ odi.
\v 4 Ya̠a̠, igiel bho̠ A̠zib̠a̠ Witenemeni d̠i̠yar a̠leriom i̠yar okpon igbirigbir na̠ etula̠n d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠,
\v 5 sa̠ i̠yar u̠te̠i̠ itenemeni d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ d̠o̠yo̠. Na̠ o̠d̠u̠a d̠o̠ d̠a̠ ib̠eb̠i ya̠ i̠yar ugir, ya̠a̠ ad̠u̠a ku d̠a̠ igbirigbir d̠o̠yo̠ sa̠ i̠na a̠tenemeni i̠yar. I̠na awo̠l d̠a̠ E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ a̠titol i̠karabh d̠i̠yar, sa̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠yar omom i̠mara, na̠ omom a̠ghud̠um.
\v 6 I̠na awo̠l d̠a̠ A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st Witenemeni d̠i̠yar a̠bhin onyen ologi a̠zuom i̠yar E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠,
\v 7 ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ o̠b̠ab̠alame̠ni̠ i̠yar d̠a̠ igbirigbir d̠o̠yo̠, ma̠ ola̠ i̠yar na̠ onwuna̠ ma̠ eb̠em ologi od̠e ad̠i̠a a̠ghud̠um kid̠ud̠ul.
\p 
\v 8 Onon a̠ga̠i o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠, sa̠ ami̠ na̠ abho̠ro̠gh anwa ma̠ o̠gba o̠kparame̠ni̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ ema̠ra̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ ta̠ ebhin eb̠la̠ rologi d̠awa egir ib̠eb̠i. I̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n ebhon sa̠ ta̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ asu̠o̠ inigha̠ ko̠ni̠ ko̠ni̠.
\v 9 Ya̠a̠ anwa, sigima̠ ma̠ raku̠anan obhobho i̠kpo̠, na̠ i̠re̠ma imitia̠n, na̠ o̠b̠e̠m, na̠ aku̠anan ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ oloko bho̠. Ezin bho̠, i̠ye̠ asu̠o̠ bo̠, sa̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ ogir ema̠ obhobho i̠kpo̠.
\v 10 Kikiome ma̠ o̠go̠me̠ma, ma̠ onin bo̠d̠o̠ i̠wal igiel, ka̠ a̠ten i̠se̠, sigima̠ i̠na.
\v 11 Loghome ma̠a̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ o̠ku̠a na̠ a̠mel ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ bho̠, sa̠ i̠karabh d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ esobh ase̠ ebhumeni i̠na.
\s1 A̠kikiom Na̠ Ibheleguma̠ Ekunuguma̠ bho̠
\p 
\v 12 Igiel ami̠ iruom Ate̠mas bo̠d̠o̠ Atai̠kiku̠s oru d̠oyom, bha̠ nugia̠ne ma̠ a̠ru ra̠ ate̠i̠ ami̠ d̠a̠ A̠nikopolis\f + \fr 3:12 \fq A̠nikopolis \ft E̠ma-i̠ne̠gi̠me̠ni̠ bho̠\f*, ezin bho̠ ami̠ ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ i̠se̠ ma̠ obhel okogoro bho̠.
\v 13 Wia̠ne ma̠ anu̠r alo̠gh agu̠o̠ ma̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ Aze̠nas o̠ni̠ oloko bho̠, na̠ Apo̠lo̠s ma̠ d̠a̠ e̠gi̠ d̠awa, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ abar ko o̠kparama d̠o̠ awa.
\v 14 Akpe̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom d̠i̠yar o̠tu̠ghan agu̠o̠ obhin obhel d̠awa ogir ib̠eb̠i ogir, b̠o̠ka̠ awa e̠te̠i̠ a̠ga̠i i̠di̠ar ya̠ i̠kpe̠ awa ma̠ o̠te̠i̠, kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ o̠ro̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ ko omum d̠o̠ ma̠ imuma̠.
\v 15 Eb̠la̠ ogbo ya̠ od̠i na̠ ami̠ ma̠ enen bho̠ epura̠n anwa. Pura̠ne ma̠ eb̠la̠ ra̠tologha̠n ya̠ itula̠n i̠yar bho̠, ya̠ awa na̠ i̠yar unwuna̠ ma̠ onin ologi ima̠ra̠ bho̠. E̠no̠gho̠man ta̠ A̠zib̠a e̠ro̠ na̠ eb̠la̠ inyin.
